            <h5 class="column-head" data-uuid="6368997b227b4130997922ca623c6428">Cotton Production and
                Slavery, 1800&#173;‒1860</h5>
            <p class="intro" data-uuid="7299cb22008344daadf41cc1cad1fe94">After the invention of the
                cotton gin, the amount of cotton produced each year in the United States soared.</p>
